    <published>2024-06-02T01:50:52.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-06-02T01:55:09.277Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>关键词:突然恋人、突然*恋人，Making Lovers</p><p>“无果而终”的恋爱无异于虚度年华。<br>山盟海誓方为恋爱正解。</p><p>若相恋，请与梦中情人来一场一生一世的恋爱。<br>看着与身边对象讴歌短暂青春的同学们身影，我如此坚信着。<br>然而，在迎来二年级暑假时，我终于意识到，梦中情人并不会从天而降。<br>想要恋爱，不是想象中梦幻般的，而是真真切切的恋爱。</p><p>梦想白首偕老的青梅竹马<br>希冀邂逅白马王子同班同学<br>憧憬人生偶像般恋爱达人的学妹<br>期望让重要的家人看到幸福未来的学姐</p><p>与她们相遇，是无数次偶然的结果。<br>重要的是此刻开始行动起来。<br>那么，我的恋情现在开始不就好了？<br>在解开最终问题之前，答案仍然未知。<br>将偶然变成命运的，取决于我自身——。</p><p><img src="https://r2.touchgal.net/2023/12/d22cb45e8120231221155924-1024x576.jpg"></img></p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/ADV%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%BD%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92/onedrive/adv_lib_001/Making%EF%BC%8ALovers/Steam%E7%89%88%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96/Making%EF%BC%8ALovers_Steam%E7%89%88%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96.part1.rar"   title="part1"><i class="red larger"></i><span>part1</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/ADV%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%BD%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92/onedrive/adv_lib_001/Making%EF%BC%8ALovers/Steam%E7%89%88%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96/Making%EF%BC%8ALovers_Steam%E7%89%88%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96.part2.rar"   title="part2"><i class="red larger"></i><span>part2</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/ADV%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%BD%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92/onedrive/adv_lib_001/Making%EF%BC%8ALovers/Steam%E7%89%88%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96/Making%EF%BC%8ALovers_Steam%E7%89%88%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96.part3.rar"   title="part3"><i class="red larger"></i><span>part3</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/ADV%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%BD%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92/onedrive/adv_lib_001/Making%EF%BC%8ALovers/Steam%E7%89%88%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96/Making%EF%BC%8ALovers_Steam%E7%89%88%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96.part4.rar"   title="part4"><i class="red larger"></i><span>part4</span></a><span class="hide-inline"><button type="button" class="hide-button" style="backgroun